show.sharing_text: हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा
show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा। 
https://links.kukufm.com/cdu54d
show.description: John is an ordinary man who wants a dignified life. but when he was insulted and denied his salary, he fought against his boss and was brutally killed by him. When everyone thought John was gone, a miracle happened. It's a second chance for not only John, but it's a war against good and bad
